parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Weak and Prone to Bending Aluminum Alloy Rims
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the aluminum alloy rims can cause tire air leaks, loss of tire pressure, and uneven tire wear, leading to accidents, loss of control, and potentially catastrophic consequences.
symptoms: when driving over potholes or normal road conditions; tire air leaks or loss of pressure; uneven tire wear; wheels become disfigured or dented; vehicle pulls to one side or vibrates while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy or deploy improperly.
symptoms: The SRS light illuminates on the dashboard
the airbags do not deploy in a crash
the airbag warning light comes on and off intermittently
the airbag system is replaced multiple times
and the vehicle is involved in a crash with no airbag deployment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the SRS light on the dashboard can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which may lead to airbag failure or improper deployment in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The SRS light comes on and stays on
the SRS light comes on and off intermittently
the airbag system is replaced multiple times
and the vehicle is involved in a crash with no airbag deployment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbags to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbags do not deploy in a crash
the vehicle is involved in a crash with no airbag deployment
and the airbag system is replaced multiple times.
